<template>
  <u-chart constructor-type="stockChart" :options="options" :fetching="fetching" :resize="resize" v-on="$listeners" />
</template>
<script>
  import UChart, { uChartProps } from '../UChart'

  export default {
    components: { UChart },
    props: {
      // highcharts options object
      options: { type: Object, required: true },

      // common options passed to base chart
      ...uChartProps,
    },
  }
</script>
